<title type="html"><![CDATA[What the industry's publications say about Classic Shell]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=385&amp;p=1979#p1979"><![CDATA[
<span style="color:#ff0000;">● <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/search.php?keywords=Reviews&amp;terms=all&amp;author=&amp;sv=0&amp;sc=1&amp;sf=titleonly&amp;sk=t&amp;sd=d&amp;sr=topics&amp;st=0&amp;ch=300&amp;t=0&amp;submit=Search" class="postlink"><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: 116%;"><strong>Read user reviews</strong></span></a> <br /><br /></span><strong><span style="color:#ff0000;">● &quot;<a href="http://winaero.com/blog/15-reasons-to-use-classic-shells-start-menu-in-windows-10/" class="postlink">Classic Shell is the gold standard of Start menus</a>&quot; - Winaero </span></strong><br /><br /><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>● &quot;<a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2013/04/16/dont-wait-for-windows-8-1-get-its-two-best-features-right-now/" class="postlink">Don't Wait For Windows to improve -- Get Its Former Best 'Features' Right Now</a>&quot; - Forbes <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/08/23/classic_shell_gives_windows_8_a_start_button/" class="postlink">Open source to the rescue</a>&quot; - The Register <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://lifehacker.com/5955089/how-to-bring-back-the-start-menu-in-windows-8" class="postlink">If it's customizability you want, Classic Shell is the program you want.</a>&quot; -LifeHacker <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.neowin.net/news/classic-shell-brings-classic-start-menu-to-windows-8" class="postlink">Classic Shell exemplifies one of the really great things about computers: you can customize them to your heart's content</a>&quot; -Neowin <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.ghacks.net/2012/04/02/classic-shell-adds-a-start-menu-back-to-windows-8/" class="postlink">Classic Shell is a godsend for Windows users who do not want the Metro interface, and prefer Microsoft would ship the OS without it in first place.</a>&quot; -gHacks <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.zdnet.com/two-must-have-downloads-that-make-windows-8-more-bearable-7000008760/" class="postlink">Must-have download that make Windows more bearable</a>&quot; - ZDNet <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.pcworld.com/article/2026719/review-classic-shell-brings-the-start-menu-to-windows-8-for-free.html" class="postlink">Gets the job done with no fuss, you'll probably want to stick with it.</a>&quot; - PC World&quot; <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.pcworld.com/article/2011537/bend-windows-8-to-your-will-with-these-free-tools.html" class="postlink">Classic Shell is probably the ultimate free tool for bypassing most controversial Windows features.</a>&quot; - PC World <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/window-on-windows/put-the-classic-start-menu-in-windows-7-with-classic-shell/2033" class="postlink">Classic Start Menu fans have a champion out there.</a>&quot; - TechRepublic <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/make-windows-8-suck-less-with-classic-shell/" class="postlink">Make Windows suck less</a>&quot; - MakeUseOf.com <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://windows.appstorm.net/reviews/utilities-reviews/bring-the-look-you-love-back-to-windows-8-with-classic-shell/" class="postlink">Bring The Look You Love Back To Windows</a>&quot; - AppStorm <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://betanews.com/2012/01/09/give-windows-7-the-xp-makeover-with-classic-shell-3-3/" class="postlink">Give Windows the XP/7 makeover</a>&quot; -Betanews <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.laptopmag.com/review/software/classic-shell.aspx" class="postlink">Abundantly customizable Start menu; Can duplicate the look and feel of Windows XP, Vista or 7</a>&quot; - Laptop Magazine <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.snapfiles.com/articles/get-rid-of-metro.html" class="postlink">Has a longstanding reputation and worked well for us</a>&quot; - SnapFiles.com <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.askvg.com/classic-shell-get-classic-start-menu-and-explorer-toolbar-buttons-cut-copy-paste-etc-back-in-windows-vista-and-7/" class="postlink">An awesome free utility</a>&quot; - AskVG.com (Tweaking with Vishal) <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.afterdawn.com/news/article.cfm/2012/11/10/opening_windows_8_a_tale_of_2_start_menus" class="postlink">Classic Shell should be a baseline to compare all other Start menu replacements against</a>.&quot; - AfterDawn.com <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.dedoimedo.com/computers/windows-8-classic-shell.html" class="postlink">Simply awesome. Community vs. Stupidity 1:0. Yes.</a>&quot; - Dedoimedo.com <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://www.7tutorials.com/fix-windows-explorer-annoyances-classic-shell" class="postlink">Fix Windows Explorer Annoyances with Classic Shell</a>&quot; - 7Tutorials.com <br /><br />● <a href="http://downloadsquad.switched.com/2009/12/23/get-windows-xp-style-start-menu-and-explorer-in-windows-7/" class="postlink">&quot;Do yourself a favor: download Classic Shell&quot;</a> - DownloadSquad <br /><br />● &quot;<a href="http://bgr.com/2012/08/24/windows-8-start-button-free-download/" class="postlink">Here’s how to bring the real Start button back to Windows</a>&quot; - BGR </strong><br /><br />● <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N0L4Cte56tc&amp;list=PLfIe3S79xejLDB4iMoP6C-kqEsrSdODCy" class="postlink"><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: 116%;"><strong>Classic Shell coverage on YouTube</strong></span></a></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Thu Mar 14, 2013 8:14 am</p><hr />
